OL,5,G1900 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,6,     FThe Amazon is where Ben's own
OL,7,     Fadventures began. Now he is back
OL,8,     Fto meet Chris, a Scotsman who has
OL,9,     Fmade his home in the most remote
OL,10,     Farea of this jungle.
OL,11,G2000 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,12,     FTravelogue series meeting people
OL,13,     Fwho gave up the rat race for an
OL,14,     Falternative lifestyle. Native
OL,15,     FItalian Annalisa is developing a
OL,16,     Fforest hideaway on the fringes of
OL,17,     Fsociety.
